## Instructions
1. List methods used with `method_name`, `method_category` (e.g. "supervised learning", "optimization"), and `is_novel` (true if proposed in this paper).
2. List baseline methods compared against.
3. List evaluation metrics used (e.g. "accuracy", "F1", "BLEU").
4. List datasets used with name, URL (if mentioned), size, and domain.
